# Project Structure Guidelines

## Monorepo Structure

The project follows an Nx monorepo structure with the following organization:

### Root Directories
- `apps/`: Contains all application projects
- `libs/`: Contains shared libraries and modules
  - `database/`: Database management and migrations
  - `shared/`: Common types, enums, and utilities

### Backend Structure (apps/backend)
- `src/modules/{module-name}/`: Module-based organization
  - `entities/`: Entity definitions for the module
  - `admin/services/`: Admin-specific service patterns
  - `frontend/services/`: Frontend-specific service patterns
  - `{module-name}.module.ts`: Module definition file

### tRPC Structure (apps/backend/src/modules/trpc)
- `routers/`: tRPC route definitions
  - `admin/`: Protected admin routes
  - `index.ts`: Route exports
- `interfaces/`: Service interfaces
- `contexts/`: Context

### Frontend Structure (apps/frontend/src)
- `assets/`: Styles, SCSS, CSS
- `components/`: Vue components
- `composables/`: TypeScript logic files (useX.ts)
- `i18n/locales/`: Translation files
- `layouts/`: Layout components
- `middleware/`: Nuxt middleware
- `pages/`: Page components
- `plugins/`: Nuxt plugins
- `public/`: Static assets
- `utils/`: Helper functions

### Admin Structure (apps/admin)
Follows similar structure to frontend

### API Structure (apps/api)
External API endpoints for third-party integrations

## Key Files
- [apps/backend/src/modules/entities.ts](mdc:apps/backend/src/modules/entities.ts): Entity registration
- [libs/database/src/migrations](mdc:libs/database/src/migrations): Database migrations
- [package.json](mdc:package.json): Project scripts and dependencies

